SPECS:
1) User can select options for size of pizza:
  Options: Small, Medium, Large
2) User can select toppings:
  Options: Tomatoes, Spinach, Onions, Mushrooms, Carrots, Sprouts, Kale,
  Olives, Beets, Mixed Greens, Peppers,
3) Pizza without toppings will return a base price:
  Input: Small
  Output: $8.99
  Input: Medium
  Output: $11.99
  Input: Large
  Output: $14.99
4) For each topping, $.99 will be added to the selected base price:
  Input: small + tomatoes + peppers
  Output: $10.99
